https://www.applovin.com/privacy
. Standard Contractual Clauses are used to transfer your data to AppLovin Corporation to ensure that they are properly protected.
8 - Managing support and contact requests
This type of service allows us to manage support and contact requests received via email or by other means, such as the contact form. The categories of personal data processed depend on the information provided by the user in the messages and the means used for communication.
Zendesk
Zendesk is a support and contact request management service provided by Zendesk Inc. Address: 989 Market Street, San Francisco, CA 94103, United States of America. Relevant privacy policy of Zendesk Inc:
https://www.zendesk.com/company/agreements-and-terms/privacy-notice/
. Standard Contractual Clauses are used to transfer your data to Zendesk Inc. to ensure that they are properly protected.
9 - Email services
We may share your data with email services that provide us with tools to send bulk emails and implement email marketing.
Brevo
